data.description: Fully renovated, NO HOA fees, large corner lot, new metal roof and new A/C make this home one of a kind. With Florida's first Great Wolf Lodge resort scheduled to open by the summer of 2024, located just around the corner, this property will be a great opportunity for all of the Airbnb investors. Gorgeous bathroom and kitchen, LED lighting throughout and a game room are some of the best features this home has to offer.   Don't let this amazing opportunity pass you by. For the right candidate, the Sellers are offering the "rent to own" option at this time ( 20% down )  There's currently a month-to-month lease in place for $4,000.00/month.
